{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/return-a-value-from-a-function-with-return","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"basic-javascript","demoType":null,"title":"Vrati Vrednost iz Funkcije Pomocu Return","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Mozemo proslediti vrednosti funkciji koristeci <dfn>argumente</dfn>. Mozete koristiti <code>return</code> naredbu da posaljete vrednost nazad iz funkcije.</p>\n<p><strong>Mfano</strong></p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">function plusThree(num) {\n  return num + 3;\n}\n\nconst answer = plusThree(5);\n</code></pre>\n<p><code>answer</code> ima vrednost <code>8</code>.</p>\n<p><code>plusThree</code> prima <dfn>argument</dfn> <code>num</code> i vraca vrednost <code>num + 3</code>.</p>\n</section>","id":"56533eb9ac21ba0edf2244c2","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Napravite funkciju <code>timesFive</code> koja prima jedan argument, mnozi ga sa <code>5</code> i vraca novu vrednost.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"JavaScript","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":18271,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/return-a-value-from-a-function-with-return"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>timesFive</code> treba da bude funkcija</p>","testString":"assert(typeof timesFive === 'function');"},{"text":"<p><code>timesFive(5)</code> treba da vrati <code>25</code></p>","testString":"assert(timesFive(5) === 25);"},{"text":"<p><code>timesFive(2)</code> treba da vrati <code>10</co